{"tid":2207171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國務次卿抵台 明悼李登輝  未提台美經濟對話 今晤蔡英文","createTime":"2020-09-18T04:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T05:54:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"475249a5310c8beaf6dccb0d11bddc105aab3231","tid":2207171,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200918/JAPTCBHIXRDVDIYWMJANJOML5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200918%2FJAPTCBHIXRDVDIYWMJANJOML5Q%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=a010c64d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200918%2FJAPTCBHIXRDVDIYWMJANJOML5Q%2F&h=e0b975e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200918/JAPTCBHIXRDVDIYWMJANJOML5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美國務次卿抵台 明悼李登輝 <br />\n未提台美經濟對話 今晤蔡英文<br />\n<br />\n【美台交流】美國國務院次卿克拉奇（Keith Krach）昨午抵台，展開一連三日訪台之旅。他是美台斷交41年以來，美國國務院派遣訪台最高級別官員。克拉奇今將與蔡英文會面，明出席悼念台灣已故總統李登輝活動。台媒期待的「台美經濟與商業對話」不在公開議程當中，台經濟部指仍會閉門交流。在克拉奇訪台前夕，兩架解放軍軍機進入台灣防空識別區。國際關係學者分析，克拉奇訪台是試探中國底線一着，只表態出席李登輝追思儀式，讓美國可在對華留有調整空間。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美大使晤台處長 撐參與聯國<br />\n<br />\n克拉奇率領的代表團昨午抵達台北松山機場，展開一連三日的訪台。台灣外交部指上月初已提出希望美方派遣現任高官，參加李登輝的追思禮拜，美方如願派國務院次卿克拉奇訪台，創下自1979年以來，訪台層級最高的國務院官員。<br />\n<br />\n克拉奇今將與台灣總統蔡英文會面，台方晚上會在總統官邸設宴，明日克拉。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TDiFWUT-nJxwrXsJdFIPoBa24J8=/2078x2953/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P4MJGI5LSRGBBG36CSYBCOXR64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTDiFWUT-nJxwrXsJdFIPoBa24J8%3D%2F2078x2953%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP4MJGI5LSRGBBG36CSYBCOXR64.jpg&h=3aa1336f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國國務院次卿克拉奇（左）昨搭專機抵達松山機場，台外交部次長曾厚仁到場接機。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家指留餘地試華底線<br />\n<br />\n台灣政府上月底宣佈放寬美豬美牛進口，美國國務院隨即宣佈創立美台雙邊經濟暨商業對話，並交由克拉奇主持。這次是這兩個月以來，第二位訪台的美國高級別官員。上月9日，美國衞生部長阿札爾（Alex Michael Azar II）訪台，其間會見蔡英文，簽署台美醫衞合作備忘錄（MOU）。由於美國國務院專責外交，故克拉奇到訪也別具意義。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡國立大學政治系副教授莊嘉穎對本報分析，這次美國派出國務次卿。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/B2wjSVvea4SqSaXY0lqXFUekBnU=/1866x1480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WDZUYWKF5VDMBEQ63PF6JDZYSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FB2wjSVvea4SqSaXY0lqXFUekBnU%3D%2F1866x1480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWDZUYWKF5VDMBEQ63PF6JDZYSQ.jpg&h=b6a0e2bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■克拉奇一行昨乘搭小型行政專機C-37A抵台。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩共機闖台防空識別區<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部昨對再有美國。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院亞太助卿史達偉（David Stilwell）也在參議院外交委員會的一份聽證會證詞批評，中國最近在全球採取的行動是「無法無天的欺凌行為」。他指，美國不是要求其他國家選邊站，而是希望各國站起來，對抗中國「邪惡的」行為，以及保護自己的主權和經濟利益。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網/中央社"},{"pid":"86b5a8b05b41d53e8c0122c14cbb69337ca1af3f","tid":2207171,"uid":369598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"口交部: 好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113ac2797851506f3d3b39c759cac5ccc6ab7c2f","tid":2207171,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86b5a8b05b41d53e8c0122c14cbb69337ca1af3f","tid":2207171,"uid":369598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"口交部: 好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:09:59.000Z","msg":"保皇黨：好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6d6b858d0ce26c852b382031070d4aafeb9720","tid":2207171,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"113ac2797851506f3d3b39c759cac5ccc6ab7c2f","tid":2207171,"uid":127575,"like":1,"disl